# Resources for Indiana Events

A collection of resources related to events in Indiana, organized by type and region.

## Statewide Event Listings

* [Festival Country Indiana](https://www.festivalcountryindiana.com/festivals-and-events)
* [GoSoIN](https://www.gosoin.com/things-to-do/events/)
* [Visit Indiana](https://visitindiana.com/events/)

## City/Region Specific Resources

### Indianapolis
* [Indy with Kids](https://indywithkids.com/free-indiana-museum-days/)
* [Visit Indy](https://www.visitindy.com/indianapolis-events)

### Bloomington
* [Visit Bloomington](https://www.visitbloomington.com/events/)

### Fort Wayne
* [Visit Fort Wayne](https://visitfortwayne.com/events/)

### South Bend
* [Visit South Bend](https://www.visitsouthbend.com/events/)

## Additional Resources

* [Hamilton County Events](https://www.visithamiltoncounty.com/cities/carmel/events/)
* [Indiana State Parks Events](https://www.in.gov/dnr/state-parks/programs/events-calendar/)
